1
00:01:23,680 --> 00:01:24,640
I beg you.

2
00:01:26,520 --> 00:01:27,520
Take her away.

3
00:01:28,160 --> 00:01:28,960
Hmph.

4
00:01:29,360 --> 00:01:33,320
I never expected Your Highness to beg me personally.

5
00:01:34,320 --> 00:01:36,920
You are truly foolish.

6
00:01:37,880 --> 00:01:39,280
I was merely using her

7
00:01:39,600 --> 00:01:41,280
to help me develop poisons.

8
00:01:42,320 --> 00:01:43,360
But she refused.

9
00:01:44,240 --> 00:01:45,640
Since she refused,

10
00:01:45,759 --> 00:01:48,320
I have no choice but to refine her into medicine,

11
00:01:48,320 --> 00:01:50,560
so she won't oppose me in the future.

12
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:51,360
You...

13
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:52,800
Since you

14
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:56,320
refuse to help Lord Yan, you oppose him instead.

15
00:01:57,039 --> 00:01:57,680
Then,

16
00:01:58,120 --> 00:02:01,360
you will become test subjects for my poison arts.

17
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:02,720
Hurry up.

18
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:04,600
Swallow the poisonous bugs.

19
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:07,480
No.

20
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:33,880
You weren't drugged.

21
00:02:34,760 --> 00:02:36,320
You dared to deceive me.

22
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:37,960
All is fair in war.

23
00:02:38,160 --> 00:02:39,560
I just played along.

24
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:42,690
Otherwise, how would I know your entire plan?

25
00:02:43,480 --> 00:02:45,240
Chuyun regards you as her benefactor,

26
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:46,440
and is devoted to you.

27
00:02:46,480 --> 00:02:49,680
Yet you treat her as a vessel for breeding poisonous bugs.

28
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:51,160
You have absolutely no conscience.

29
00:02:51,160 --> 00:02:52,400
You are heartless.

30
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:53,440
Hmph.

31
00:02:55,880 --> 00:02:56,680
Chuyun?

32
00:02:57,480 --> 00:02:59,840
I killed Chuyun's entire family.

33
00:03:00,160 --> 00:03:01,480
Sparing her life

34
00:03:01,880 --> 00:03:04,000
was my greatest mercy.

35
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:06,440
People like you

36
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:08,560
know nothing of benevolence

37
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:09,360
or love.

38
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:12,600
All you care about are your own selfish desires.

39
00:03:12,600 --> 00:03:13,120
Love?

40
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:15,520
It is nothing more

41
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:18,000
than a fleeting illusion.

42
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,680
Only power

43
00:03:20,079 --> 00:03:20,960
and status

44
00:03:21,600 --> 00:03:22,760
are eternal.

45
00:03:23,480 --> 00:03:24,280
Today,

46
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:27,120
none of you will leave here alive.

47
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:28,840
If you want to keep us here,

48
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:30,960
let's see if you have what it takes.

49
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:34,960
Lord Zhou.

50
00:03:35,840 --> 00:03:37,120
Lord Zhou.

51
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:38,980
This...

52
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:41,360
Why isn't Lord Yan in the study?

53
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:43,560
I've found the Young Master's whereabouts.

54
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:44,160
Lord Zhou,

55
00:03:44,440 --> 00:03:45,700
you are a step too late.

56
00:03:45,920 --> 00:03:48,560
Lord Yan has personally gone to find the Young Master

57
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:49,560
to bring him back.

58
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:52,170
Lord Yan has already taken action.

59
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,920
How is that possible?

60
00:03:56,480 --> 00:03:57,000
No.

61
00:03:57,160 --> 00:03:58,320
I must go check.

62
00:03:58,840 --> 00:03:59,440
Lord Zhou.

63
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:04,800
Lord Zhou

64
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:06,360
really is impatient.

65
00:04:09,720 --> 00:04:10,720
Where is Divine Doctor Ji?

66
00:04:10,720 --> 00:04:12,080
Go get her quickly.

67
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:12,840
Lord Zhou,

68
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:15,120
Divine Doctor Ji hasn't shown up today.

69
00:04:15,120 --> 00:04:16,680
Hall Master Du is nowhere to be found,

70
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:18,540
so I'm afraid you'll have to wait.

71
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:20,800
What am I going to do?

72
00:04:21,880 --> 00:04:23,760
