109
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:09,560
However,

110
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:11,480
I later learned

111
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:14,400
that Duyu had refined a mind-controlling venomous insect.

112
00:06:14,400 --> 00:06:16,360
So as long as I control you,

113
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:17,880
everything the Prince of Zhenbei has

114
00:06:17,880 --> 00:06:19,280
