119
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:30,360
The new Emperor has always wanted to clear our names.

120
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:31,760
You don't have to do this.

121
00:06:32,080 --> 00:06:33,040
Clear our names?

122
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:36,810
